{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b649548189","title":"天津大学学生的大字报","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"601a10a139","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"b649548189"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"174744163f","name":"《内部参考》"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"91dedbd318","type":"title","text":"天津大学学生的大字报","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b649548189"},{"id":"1ec4200b5a","type":"authors","text":"《内部参考》","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b649548189"},{"id":"e09e0eb900","type":"paragraph","text":"天大一些学生提出带有政治性问题的有：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b649548189"},{"id":"635d5d7db6","type":"paragraph","text":"1、取消学校中的党委会、团委会，由教师和学生组成校务会议来领导学校。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b649548189"},{"id":"e578583c5b","type":"paragraph","text":"2、团的干部是政治流氓，团委会应受学生会领导。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b649548189"},{"id":"34a7394ff3","type":"paragraph","text":"3、改组人民日报和中国青年报。人民日报应该由全国各党派、人民团体、民主人士参加，而不应由共产党操纵。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b649548189"},{"id":"9e39b15f21","type":"paragraph","text":"4、在高等学校中不应肃反，发动群众搞肃反刺伤了教师和学生的心灵。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b649548189"},{"id":"cb921de870","type":"paragraph","text":"5、三大主义的根源是民主集中制。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b649548189"},{"id":"8b657e2ebc","type":"paragraph","text":"6、宪法是挂羊头卖狗肉，民主是“金鱼缸式”的民主。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b649548189"},{"id":"9cd3723ec2","type":"paragraph","text":"7、必修政治课违反信仰自由的政策。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b649548189"},{"id":"58548ebc28","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源:1957年6月13日新华通讯社编《内部参考》。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b649548189"}],"page":{"id":"fe08128893","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b649548189","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}